data.description: OPEN HOUSE: SAT (12/16) 11AM TO 3PM. Assumable FHA loan option at 3.625% interest rate; less than 1 mile from the boat ramp! This charming 2018 year-built, 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence boasts an enticing blend of stone and siding exterior, creating an eye-catching and timeless facade that captures the essence of this serene lakeside community. Nestled in a low HOA fee neighborhood, this 1,288 square foot gem is strategically located just minutes from the glistening waters of Canyon Lake, offering endless opportunities for recreational activities and scenic views. The spacious open floor plan is thoughtfully designed for both comfortable living and seamless entertaining. Vaulted ceilings add an extra touch of grandeur, creating a sense of space and airiness. The interior features ceramic tile flooring throughout, ensuring easy maintenance and a cool, contemporary aesthetic. The kitchen showcases dark stained cabinetry, complementing the overall design while providing ample storage space for your culinary endeavors. Outside, you'll find a fantastic front yard and backyard space, perfect for gardening, relaxation, and creating lasting memories with friends and family. Don't miss out on this opportunity to make this beautiful home yours, where comfort, style, and lakeside living converge.
